// Man page for jack
manJack="JACK(1)                          X Shell Manual                          JACK(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    jack - initiates a local dictionary attack
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Initiates a local dictionary attack to insert the root password
    into the cache file. Pass in optional NICK[NAME].
    
    <b>REQUIREMENTS</b>
    SSH or FTP must be available on the target for jack to be
    successful. Without an available service, the attack will fail."